window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>The Slight Edge</i> describes why some people succeed in life and why others do not. Ever wonder why some people work, day in and day out, to help establish other people's dreams?</p> <p><i>The Slight Edge</i> is a new way of thinking. Learn how to make smarter choices in your daily life which will ultimately lead you to the path of your own success.&nbsp;</p> <p>In this summary, you will gain insight on how the author followed the philosophy of the \"slight edge\", taking control of his own life and building his own dream.</p>"; 
